  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, mix together the masarepa and pilaf.",
    "In a large bowl, beat the cream cheese until smooth.",
    "Add the eggs one at a time, beating well after each addition.",
    "Stir in the shredded cheddar (if using) and the masarepa mixture.",
    "Using a 1/4 cup measuring cup, scoop the mixture into a greased mini muffin tin.",
    "Bake for 20-25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm with a dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of chopped scallions."
